                        <interp inst="t18460706-name-96" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS HOLLOWAY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I apprehended Wright at the Black Lion public-house about half an hour after he escaped—I had seen both prisoners together between ten and eleven o'clock that morning.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Morgan's Defence.</hi> The property was given to me by a man to take to the bridge; the policeman stopped me; I immediately told him so.</p>
